Package serverSide.entities

Class AssaultPartyClientProxy

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Thread
serverSide.entities.AssaultPartyClientProxy
All Implemented Interfaces:
MasterThiefCloning, OrdinaryThiefCloning, Runnable
public class AssaultPartyClientProxy extends Thread implements MasterThiefCloning, OrdinaryThiefCloning
Service provider agent for access to the Assault Party. Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
